article_title: Don’t Mine for Fool’s Gold in Your Fantasy League
article_text:
Tampa Bay Buccaneers tight end Austin Seferian-Jenkins and Green Bay Packers wideout James Jones are likely to be the most popular players in fantasy football this week. That’s because both players, who were largely ignored in fantasy drafts before the season, had huge games in Week 1 making them prime targets on the waiver wire.

But history says a healthy level of skepticism is warranted for Week 1 wonders, who often fail to live...
